Package org.apache.openjpa.persistence.meta

Class Members

java.lang.Object
org.apache.openjpa.persistence.meta.Members
public class Members extends Object
Persistent attribute according to JPA 2.0 metamodel. Implemented as a thin adapter to OpenJPA FieldMetadata. Mostly immutable.
Since:
2.0.0
Author:
Pinaki Poddar
